name: fromis_9 Jiheon
description:
If you like my LoRAs please consider to support me by buying me a coffee here so I can make a new LoRA faster. I do open commissions there too if you want to make your own custom LoRA.

Trigger word: fromisjiheon

Use CLIP SKIP 2. You may need to use HIRES FIX with denoise strength between 0.5-0.7, Hires steps 20-30 is good but you can use whatever you want. Upscaler use 4x Foolhardy Remacri or SWINIR 4x.

Best checkpoints/models to use:

Realistic: VisionGen, ChillOutMix, ArtEros, Snapdd00, Henrealmix

Fanart/painting style: Dreamshaper, LucidMix, SunshineMix, Majicmix

Use it wisely. I don't responsible for anything you generated with this LoRa.

modelVersions.name: fromis_9 Jiheon - v2
modelVersions.description:
2nd version. Trained on latest version of Linaqruf's colab using 30 images with HassanBlend 1.4 as its base model.

I use new settings for this, it's better in realistic and face similarity than the previous settings but it's harder to stylize it especially hair colors and painting style. Best at close-up, pose will be repetitive at some seeds and prompts because its dataset have many similar pose, but it can be solved with Controlnet, the face similarity will be decrease though.
